Step1: Download vagrant
Stpe2: Install vagrant
Step3: Install VirtualBox
Step4: Create a Vagrant file of Your OS which needs to be download
create a file name "Vagrantfile" without .txt format
=================
Vagrant.configure("2") do |config|
  config.vm.box = "centos/7"
end
=================
Step5: Run below command on Dos prompt and current location should be the path of "Vagrantfile".
C:> vagrant up

Step6: To connect with Virtual Machine
C:> vagrant ssh

Step7: Check Virtual machihne on Vitualbox

Default username: root
Default password: vagrant

